  "text": " It's more American flavor. You get a country-ish western soundtrack while as it depicts a Japanese character in a Japanese setting. It really shows the director's bias. And as a manga first viewer myself, it's very hard to wave away these criticisms because the adaptation is proving that it's prioritizing style and in this case a homage to the manga's original weight and intent.",
